<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>すけっと ~福井県版~</title>
      <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
      <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="heading">
            <%= link_to root_path, class: 'submit' do %>
            <%= image_tag 'すけっと.png' , size: '150x50' ,class: "purchase-btn-icon" %>
            <% end %>
      </div>
        <div class="navbar">
          <ul class="nav-lists">
            <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <li>&#x1f3e0;おかえりなさい<%= current_user.nickname %>さん</li>
            <li>&#x1f933;<%= link_to user_path(current_user.id), method: :get do %><%= current_user.nickname %>さんのページ<% end %></li>
            <li>&#x1f622;<%= link_to 'ログアウト', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: "logout" %></li>
            <% else %>
            <li>&#x1f60a;<%= link_to 'ログイン', new_user_session_path, class: "login" %></li>
            <li>&#x1f60a;<%= link_to '新規登録', new_user_registration_path, class: "sign-up" %></li>
            <li>&#x1f60a;ふるさとの納税サービス</li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
    </header>
      <div class="contents">
        <div class="first-view">
          <%= image_tag "top.png", class:"top-image" %>
        </div>
          <p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>
            <div class="girl_center">
              <div class="girl_talk_set">
                <div class="icon-box">
                  <%= image_tag "girl.png", size: '40x40'  ,class:"girl-icon" %>
                </div>
                  <div class="girl_talk">みんなのありがとう</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <p></p><p></p><p></p>
      <div class="upper-content"> 
        <ul class="messages">
          <li class="message">
            <div class="message-date">2020/01/03</div>
            <div>坂井市の東尋坊で<b>ふれあい広場の手伝い</b></div>
          </li>
          <li class="message">
            <div class="message-date">2020/01/02</div>
            <div>福井市の故郷老人ホームで<b>書き初め大会</b></div>
          </li>
          <li class="message">
            <div class="message-date">2019/12/24</div>
            <div>福井市の故郷老人ホームで<b>クリスマス会</b></div>
          </li>
          <li class="message">
            <div class="message-date">2019/11/15</div>
            <div>越前市の今村さん宅で<b>越前ガニ収穫後みんなで食事</b></div>
          </li>
          <li class="message">
            <div class="message-date">2019/10/28</div>
            <div>鯖江市の内藤さん宅で<b>キャベツ収穫</b></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p></p><p></p><p></p>
        <div class="girl_center">
          <div class="girl_talk_set">
            <div class="icon-box">
              <%= image_tag "girl.png", size: '40x40'  ,class:"girl-icon" %>
            </div>
              <div class="girl_talk">みんなのお手伝い</div>
          </div>
        </div>
          <div class="middle-content">
           <ul class='item-lists'>
             <% if @posts.present? %>
               <% @posts.each do |post| %>
                 <li class='list'>
                   <div class="thanx">
                      <div class='item-img-content'>
                        <video src=<%= rails_blob_path(post.video) %> type="video", controls></video>
                          <% if post.post_order.present?  %>
                            <p class="text">お手伝いありがとう</p>
                          <% end %>
                      </div>
                   </div>
                  <div class='item-info'>
                    <h3 class='item-name'>
                      <%= link_to post_path(post.id) do %>
                        <%= post.user.nickname %>さんを助けに行く<% end %><h2>依頼→<%= post.title %>
                          <span>&#x1f4b0;お小遣い→<%= post.price %>円<br></span>
                    </h3></h2>
                  </div>
                </li>
              <% end %>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      <div>
    <div class="bottom-content">
      <form class="contact-form">
        <div class="girl_center">
          <div class="girl_talk_set">
            <div class="icon-box">
              <%= image_tag "girl.png", size: '40x40'  ,class:"girl-icon" %>
            </div>
              <div class="girl_talk">お手伝いを依頼する？</div>
              </div>
          </div>
            <p></p>
          <%= link_to new_post_path, class: 'submit' do %>
            <%= image_tag 'icon_camera.png' , size: '280x250' ,class: "purchase-btn-icon" %>
          <% end %>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
  <footer>
    <p>すけっと ~福井県版~ </p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>